    <h2>Frequently Asked Questions</h2>

    <p><strong>What types of projects has Engg-Tech completed in Singapore?</strong><br>
    Engg-Tech has completed projects across Singapore including hospitals, MRT depots, warehouses, condominiums, churches, army camps, commercial buildings and government facilities.</p>

    <p><strong>Has Engg-Tech worked on large-scale or government projects?</strong><br>
    Yes. Engg-Tech has completed projects at Sengkang General Hospital, Tuas West MRT Extension Depot, Seletar Airport Warehouse, Bedok Waterworks PUB Pump Station, and various army camps and government facilities across Singapore.</p>

    <p><strong>Does Engg-Tech handle residential projects such as HDB and condominiums?</strong><br>
    Yes. In addition to commercial and industrial projects, Engg-Tech has completed works at condominiums including The Garden Residences, Parc Komo, Pearl Bank Condominium, One Holland Village Residence, and CASA ARE Condominium.</p>

    <p><strong>How can I engage Engg-Tech for a new project?</strong><br>
    Contact Engg-Tech by emailing <a href="mailto:info@engg-tech.com">info@engg-tech.com</a> or via the <a href="/contact-us/">enquiry form</a>. Our team will review your project requirements and respond within 1 business day.</p>

